<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, June 5 (Xinhua) -- The United States said on Monday
that the Lockerbie case would not be affected by an assertion that
Iran was behind the Pam Am flight bomb plot, but said it would
follow evidence wherever it leads.
</P>
<P>
