leads. That's always been our position. Right now, we are
assessing credibility of any information that may be provided,"
Reeker said.
</P>
<P>
He said Washington had made clear it would not discuss the case
in detail while the case is going on. It is being held at Camp
Zeist in the Netherlands under Scottish law. 
