said on Monday that the 17th meeting of the Damascus Declaration
signatories took up important issues in a constructive and
objective manner, breathing new life into the declaration.
</P>
<P>
At the end of the two-day foreign ministers meeting held here,
Moussa told a press conference that there was "complete and all-out
support" for the Palestinian and Syrian stances on the Middle East
peace process.
</P>
<P>
