Blix,in his mission of resuming U.N. disarmament inspection in
Iraq.
</P>
<P>
During a meeting with the UNMOVIC chief in Paris, French
Foreign Minister Hubert Vedrine said France would help him achieve
his task through different means, according to French Foreign
Ministry spokeswoman Anne Gazeau-Secret.
</P>
