The 10th G-15 exhibition is aimed at boosting and encouraging
trade exchange among the group's member states, the official in
charge of international exhibitions said.
</P>
<P>
Seminars and workshops will be held during the exhibition in a
bid to exchange views of economic development and introduce trade
and investment opportunities in the group's members, Saleh said.
</P>
<P>
