<P>
The Xinhua article stressed that that it was only because of
the consensus that a series of negotiations became possible
between the two sides of the Straits, including the talks between
the heads of ARATS and SEF.
</P>
<P>
It's inconceivable that some people participating in the
negotiations could publicly deny the existing basis for the
