<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, June 5 (Xinhua) -- New Zealand Minister of Foreign
Affairs and Trade Phil Goff issued a statement here Monday,
calling for resolving the ethnic tensions in the Solomon Islands
by dialogue.
</P>
<P>
New Zealand is monitoring the situation developing in the
Solomon Islands and working "to endeavor to get the parties
together to resolve ethnic tensions by dialogue," Goff said.
