-- Eight Chinese Airlines will purchase 100 planes from Airbus,
84 of which are in operation now, said Jean-Michel Bellier, vice
president of Airbus China Corporation Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
-- The Bank of China (BOC) has raised deposit and lending rates
for four major foreign currencies -- U.S. dollar, British pound,
euro and HK dollar, as well as the deposit rates for Canadian
dollar and Swiss franc in China.
</P>
