Turkey will take up a home away from home as they have chosen
the Turkish community in Delden which is situated in Holland close
to the German border.
</P>
<P>
Outsiders Slovenia have chosen modest accommadation in another
Dutch town of Soestduinen.
</P>
<P>
Most nations will quit the country the day after elimination.
