disposed of Asa Carlsson of Sweden 6-2, 6-1. Marta Marrero, a 17-
year-old qualifier from Spain, defeated qualifier Rossana De Los
Rios 4-6, 6-0, 6-4. Fifth seed Conchita Martinez cruised past Ai
Sugiyama of Japan 5-7, 6-3, 6-4. 
