first was prevented when goalkeeper Roberto Bonano raced out of
his goal to stop Roger Suarez with a crude foul for which he was
booked.
</P>
<P>
In the 38th minute, Bonano could only watch helplessly as a
Suarez shot flew a hair's breadth wide of his post.
</P>
<P>
The Bolivians were left with one point from their three matches.
