<HEADLINE> Chilean President Visits Rain Affected Zone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTIAGO, June 5 (Xinhua) -- Chilean President Ricardo Lagos
inspected Monday south of the country where rains have left
thousands victims.
</P>
<P>
Before his visit to Valdivia, the area most affected by floods,
Lagos said he will decide what places would be declared
catastrophe areas so that they will receive more resources and
assistance.
