The ONEMI sent Valdivia four buses with 600 mats, 1,200
blankets and 600 foodstuff boxes.
</P>
<P>
Lagos met Monday for an hour and a half with authorities from
the Justice Department in order to evaluate the situation and
rescue operations. 
