institutions and the United Nations provide an important means of
assisting the region to participate effectively in the new global
economy while managing social change.
</P>
<P>
Janneh will also meet the challenges of contributing
effectively to the implementation of UNDP's business plans.
</P>
<P>
He came to UNDP as a development planner from the Government of
Gambia.  
