<HEADLINE> Wall Street Stocks End Mixed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, June 5 (Xinhua) -- Wall Street stocks ended mixed
Monday as investors rewarded technology companies with good
earnings while took some profits from last week's big gains.
</P>
